name: All Things Must Pass
description:
I felt myself being controlled by the chaos in my brain, sleepless, stupid thoughts, anxiety, and guilt. And then i got help, i got chemical angels to help me stay alive. I was very helpful but i hated it, then i tried to swear to myself, that i will prove it and i will find myself.
